net.sf.sprockets.google

Class Place

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.sprockets.google.Place
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Place.Prediction

    public class Place
extends Object
    Google Place returned from a Places method. The properties which are populated will vary according to the Places method called and the Fields provided. Check the Places method documentation for the available fields. Properties that have not been populated will return null, when possible, or the default value will be specified in the method documentation.
